plot: The Mandalorian braves high seas and meets unexpected allies.

Continuing the search for other Mandalorians, Din and The Child find themselves on the estuary moon of Trask in the Arkanis Sector, a world mostly covered by oceans, where they are to drop off their passenger, The Frog Lady. After a short time on the moon, they find themselves in the company of unexpected allies, and learn there may be more than one Way.
